snippet.title: Just Cause 4 - "One Man Did All This?" Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Pre-order Just Cause 4 now: http://www.bringsthethunder.com

After their latest humiliating defeat, a squad of wounded Black Hand soldiers attempt to explain to their leader, Gabriela Morales, how they managed to get beaten by just one man -- Rico Rodriguez.

Just Cause 4 comes to Xbox One, PlayStation® 4 and Steam PC on December 4, 2018.

Pre-order Now: https://justcause.square-enix-games.com/en-us/buy-now
Available December 4, 2018.
